question: Show science labs and art studios with computers.
sql_query1:
SELECT Science_Lab.name
FROM Science_Lab
WHERE Science_Lab.Available_Resources = "Computers"
UNION
SELECT Art_Studio.name
FROM Art_Studio
WHERE Art_Studio.Available_Resources = "Computers"
sql_query2:
SELECT Science_Lab.name
FROM Science_Lab
UNION
SELECT Art_Studio.name
FROM Art_Studio
WHERE Art_Studio.Available_Resources = "Computers"
interpretation1: Which science labs have computers and which art studios have the same available resources?
interpretation2: Provide a list of all science labs and also provide a list of all art studios with computers.
